casebody.data:
Friday, January 13, 1989

MOTION DOCKET

87- 1886. Cleveland Elec. Illum. Co. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio, No. 86-05-EL-EFC. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of the joint motion for continuance of oral argument currently scheduled for February 8, 1989, IT IS ORDERED by the court that said motion be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective January 12, 1989.
